          "date": "2013-01-18 08:24:47.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-2642 osd-ldiskfs: Unlock inode before iput",
        "message": "LU-2642 osd-ldiskfs: Unlock inode before iput\n\nCommit 250df6ed added a WARN_ON for I_NEW being set in iput_final\n(v2.6.38).\n\nosd_oi_index_create_one calls calls both iget_locked and\next4_create_inode, both of which will return an inode with I_NEW set.\n\nWith the check in iput_final, we'll hit a WARN_ON every time this\nfunction is called.\n\nWe unlock the new inode before the iput as other file systems already\ndo.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: Ie1009baf72f10297bfaeb972b865ebfcf29fb7ac\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
